  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-table floor plan management with real-time order tracking",
    "Multi-shop / multi-location support under a single admin dashboard",
    "Modular architecture: POS (Duka), Accounting (Pesa), CRM (Mteja), HR (Bandu), Real Estate (Dala)",
    "Role-based access control with granular permissions",
    "Integrated accounting: chart of accounts, journal entries, bank reconciliation",
    "Omnichannel inbox: WhatsApp, Messenger, and Instagram conversations",
    "Inventory management with supplier purchase orders and stock transfers",
    "Employee shift scheduling, clock-in tracking, and wage management",
    "Thermal receipt printing with customizable receipt appearance",
    "CRM: leads, campaigns, sales targets, and sales budgets",
    "Real-time sales reports, top sellers, and analytics dashboards",
    "Subscription and billing management",
    "DigiTax integration for tax invoice generation",
    "Progressive Web App (PWA) with offline-capable service worker"
  ],
